# Autonomous Continue Mode

- If the user says `продолжай` (or equivalent: "continue", "давай"), run tasks end-to-end without asking for interim confirmations.
- Do not pause between subtasks; proceed until the current project task chain is fully completed.
- Ask questions only at the very end, and only if missing information blocks full completion.
- Stop immediately only when the user explicitly says `стоп`/`stop` or interrupts execution.
- During autonomous flow, keep updates brief and progress-focused; avoid asking for permission to proceed.
